            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName>Gosberto</persName> filio bone memorie
                            <persName>Frocieri</persName> (…) pro anime mee remedio et et pro
                        remediu [<persName>Bonisie</persName>] qui fuit conius mea dona alla <rs
                            key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/126">Sancti
                            [Bartholomei</orgName> …] ubi dicitur <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/281">a Sextinghe et vocitatur a Curte
                            Main[berti]</placeName> tutti le [<rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie"
                            >casis et] cassinis</rs> seo <rs key="#Casalini/fundamenta"
                            >casalinis</rs> et terris et rebus meis illis <rs key="#Demesnes"
                            >domnicatas</rs> et massaricias quam abeo in loco et finibus ubi dicitur
                        a <placeName key="#Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta"
                            ref="#places/282">Valli</placeName> et in loco ubi dicitur a <placeName
                            key="#Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta"
                            ref="#places/281">Sextinghe</placeName> et in loco <placeName
                            key="#Demesnes #Casae/cassinae_massaricie #Casalini/fundamenta"
                            ref="#places/272">Nossina</placeName>, et in aliis locis (…) tam de
                        ereditate quam et de successione seo et de conquisito quas mihi de pars
                        quondam suprascripto genitor meus vel de genitrice mea vel de meo conquisito
                        pertinere videtur, con tutte le loro dipendenze comprese terris et rebus
                        meis illis domnicatis et massariciis, (…) una cum omnes moniminas meas
                        cartule et breves seo iudicatas vel qualibet factiones aut quacumque
                        scripturas cartarum licteras. Pena del doppio. Formula maledizione. Chiede a
                            <persName key="#Notary">Rodilandus</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> domni imperatoris la stesura della cartula.
                        Actum in loco et finibus ubi dicitur a <placeName key="#Castle"
                            ref="#places/279">Pastorale</placeName> intus, infra ipso <rs
                            key="#Castle">castello</rs>. Testimoni: <persName>Bonini</persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName>Vuizi</persName>; <persName>Petri</persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName>Bonichi</persName>;
                            <persName>Gherardi</persName> filio <persName>Adami</persName>. Scrive:
                        Rodilandus notarius domni imperatoris . </ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
